## Solution 5

```python
class InsufficientBalanceError(Exception):
    pass

balance = 5000
withdraw = int(input("Enter Amount: "))

if withdraw > balance:
    raise InsufficientBalanceError(
        "Insufficient Balance."
    )

balance -= withdraw

print("Remaining Balance:", balance)
